<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Flutter Development</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/node.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section">
        <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="background-video">
            <source src="https://videos.pexels.com/video-files/3130284/3130284-uhd_2560_1440_30fps.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            Your browser does not support the video tag.
        </video>
        <div class="hero-overlay">
            <h1>Flutter App Development</h1>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Flutter -->
    <section class="about-flutter">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Build Beautiful Apps with Flutter</h2>
            <p>
                Flutter is Google’s open-source UI toolkit for building natively compiled applications for mobile, web, and desktop from a single codebase. At Quickly Platforms, we specialize in developing high-performance, stunning, and scalable apps using Flutter.
            </p>
            <p>
                Whether you're launching a startup or scaling a product, Flutter ensures speed, flexibility, and a seamless user experience across all platforms.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features of Flutter -->
    <section class="flutter-features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Key Features of Flutter Development</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Single Codebase</h3>
                    <p>Write once, deploy on Android, iOS, Web, and Desktop platforms.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Fast Development</h3>
                    <p>Speed up the development cycle with Flutter’s Hot Reload feature.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Rich UI Components</h3>
                    <p>Leverage a wide range of customizable widgets for beautiful UIs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>High Performance</h3>
                    <p>Enjoy near-native performance with Dart and compiled code.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Cross-Platform Support</h3>
                    <p>Launch your app on multiple platforms without extra effort.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Integration Ready</h3>
                    <p>Integrate with APIs, Firebase, and third-party tools seamlessly.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Attractive UI/UX</h3>
                    <p>Create modern, responsive, and delightful interfaces with ease.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Open Source</h3>
                    <p>Leverage community-driven innovation and updates from Google.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Native Features Access</h3>
                    <p>Access device features like camera, GPS, and storage effortlessly.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Easy Maintenance</h3>
                    <p>Maintain and update your app efficiently with clean code architecture.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Scalability</h3>
                    <p>Build apps that grow with your user base and feature set.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Backed by Google</h3>
                    <p>Develop with confidence using a toolkit supported by a tech giant.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="call-to-action">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready to Build Your App with Flutter?</h2>
            <p>
                Contact our team today to discuss your project and leverage Flutter for fast, beautiful, and scalable app development.
            </p>
            <a href="/Getintouch" class="btn-connect">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
